uge). MV4+ instants can be cast off the top at instant speed naturally."}, {"name": "Valley Floodcaller does two things", "note": "(1) flash-enables all your noncreature spells, and (2) each noncreature spell untaps your Frogs \u2014 including Glarb \u2014 for another surveil 2, letting you chain through the library in one turn."}, {"name": "Seedborn Muse", "note": "untaps Glarb and all your lands on every opponent's turn \u2014 surveil and free casts each turn cycle, and you can hold up counters without skipping development."}, {"name": "Cabal Coffers", "note": "taps for {B} per Swamp; Urborg makes every land a Swamp. 12+ lands = 12+ mana from a single Coffers tap."}, {"name": "Kokusho + Rite", "note": "the copies are legendary, all die instantly to the legend rule, each drains 5 \u2192 25 per opponent."}, {"name": "Surveil 2 is a free tap ability", "note": "use it to bin sub-4-MV cards so the top of your library stays castable."}], "composition": [{"name": "Game Changers", "count": 3}, {"name": "Extra Land Drops", "count": 4}, {"name": "Landfall Payoffs", "count": 4}, {"name": "Land Recursion", "count": 5}, {"name": "Land Tutors / Ramp", "count": 12}, {"name": "Mana Acceleration", "count": 2}, {"name": "Creature Tutors", "count": 3}, {"name": "Card Advantage / Engines", "count": 1}, {"name": "Flash Enablers", "count": 1}, {"name": "Reanimation / Recursion", "count": 5}, {"name": "Finishers \u2014 Reanimation Targets", "count": 4}, {"name": "X-Spell Finisher", "count": 1}, {"name": "Copy", "count": 1}, {"name": "Counterspells", "count": 4}, {"name": "Removal / Interaction", "count": 9}, {"name": "Fog / Defense", "count": 1}, {"name": "Protection", "count": 1}, {"name": "Lands", "count": 38}], "decklist": {"total": 100, "grouped": true, "commander": {"n": "Glarb, Calamity's Augur", "gc": false}, "groups": [{"name": "Game Changers", "count": 3, "cards": [{"n": "Demonic Tutor", "gc": true}, {"n": "Fierce Guardianship", "gc": true}, {"n": "Seedborn Muse", "gc": true}]}